title: Fans Focused On Selfies At Arizona Baseball Game
text:
Fans Focused On Selfies At Arizona Baseball Game October 2, 2015, 6:23 AM PHOENIX, AZ - 
The Colorado Rockies visited the Arizona Diamondbacks on Thursday night, but the TV broadcast took time to notice a group of women and their cell phones. 
The Diamondbacks topped the Rockies 8-6, but the members of Alpha Chi Omega might not have even noticed.
